  "instructions": [
    "Heat the ghee in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the grated ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the garlic-infused oil and cook for 30 seconds.",
    "Add the kidney beans, sake, chocolate chips, salt, and black pepper, and stir well.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the lid and continue to simmer for another 10 minutes, or until the flavors have melded together.",
    "Serve hot over rice or with naan bread."
